text: Marco Zaragoza (born 25 April 1973) is a Mexican former cyclist. He competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics and the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1973 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male cyclists Category:Olympic cyclists of Mexico Category:Cyclists at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Cyclists at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
